&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-1323580" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250827_095434-1280x720.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250827_095434-scaled.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250827_095434-694x390.jpg 694w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
